code: @Test public void loadFactoriesInCorrectOrder() {     List<DummyFactory> factories = SpringFactoriesLoader.loadFactories(DummyFactory.class, null).     assertEquals(2, factories.size()).     assertTrue(factories.get(0) instanceof MyDummyFactory1).     assertTrue(factories.get(1) instanceof MyDummyFactory2). }

@Test public void loadPackagePrivateFactory() {     List<DummyPackagePrivateFactory> factories = SpringFactoriesLoader.loadFactories(DummyPackagePrivateFactory.class, null).     assertEquals(1, factories.size()).     assertTrue((factories.get(0).getClass().getModifiers() & Modifier.PUBLIC) == 0). }
